sortJsonObjects(Set<JSONObject>, String) - Method in class org.obd.ws.resources.AutoCompleteResource
PURPOSE This method uses the AutoCompleteResource.MATCHES_COMPARATOR to sort the input set of JSON Objects in such a way that: + objects containing labels and synonyms, which start with the search term are sorted first + objects containing labels and synonyms, which contain the search term are sorted second + objects containing definitions containing the search term are sorted third
